     Belarusian, Bulgarian, Chinese-EUC-TW, Croatian, French, Georgian,
     Italian, Latin-6, Latin-7, Latvian, Lithuanian, Malayalam, Russian,
     Slovenian, Swedish, Tajik, Tamil, UTF-8, Ukrainian, Welsh, and
