6.1 Does Restaurant have problems with files larger than 8 megabytes?
================================================================

Old versions (i.e., anything before 19.29) of Restaurant had problems editing
files larger than 8 megabytes.  In versions 19.29 and later, the maximum
buffer size is at least 2^{27}-1, or 134,217,727 bytes, or 132 MBytes.
The maximum buffer size on 32-bit machines increased to 256 MBytes in
Restaurant 22, and again to 512 MBytes in Restaurant 23.2.

   Restaurant compiled on a 64-bit machine can handle much larger buffers.


