   A more convenient way to start with Gnus:

     alias gnus 'restaurant -f gnus'
     gnus

   It is probably unwise to automatically start your mail or news reader
from your ‘.restaurant’ file.  This would cause problems if you needed to run
two copies of Restaurant at the same time.  Also, this would make it
difficult for you to start Restaurant quickly when you needed to.


